<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17750] S3 file download does not gracefully handle connection errors</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17750</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When downloading large object from S3, it&apos;s not uncommon to get a ConnectionClosedException or something else similar. We should be able to handle this gracefully and restart the download from the last place we have recorded.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
